s).isSameAs(String.class);\n        } finally {\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(originalClassLoader);\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void fallsBackToClassForNameWhenThreadContextClassLoaderIsAbsent() throws Exception {\n        final ClassLoader originalClassLoader = Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader();\n        Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(null);\n        try {\n            final Class<?> loadedClass = ReflectionUtils.classForName(Integer.class.getName());\n\n            assertThat(ReflectionUtils.getThreadContextClassLoader()).isNull();\n            assertThat(loadedClass).isSameAs(Integer.class);\n        } finally {\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(originalClassLoader);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2045, "output": 975, "cacheRead": 22528, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25548, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778319674579, "responseId": "resp_010af62d95833ff00169ff013b2fb8819d858b887f3a7a3cca"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_sTIypiAGWUUsFjkdG0NWKuxD|fc_010af62d95833ff00169ff01434430819d8dcb9bb7b2b832d1", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1796 bytes to tests/src/org.jboss.interceptor/jboss-interceptor-core/2.0.0.CR1/src/test/java/org_jboss_interceptor/jboss_interceptor_core/ReflectionUtilsTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778319685839}]}
